  <brief_title>Ambulatory Versus Home Blood Pressure Measurement</brief_title>
  <official_title>EVALUATION OF BLOOD PRESSURE MEASUREMENTS OUTSIDE OFFICE: COMPARISON OF DIAGNOSIS BASED ON EITHER AMBULATORY OR HOME BLOOD PRESSURE MEASUREMENTS</official_title>
