  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective study comparing the three blood pressure monitoring methods on the
      diagnosis of arterial hypertension. Blood pressure of each subject will be evaluated with
      clinic, home and 24h ambulatory blood pressure measurements in three visits
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
